Not all sunscreens work the same way—your skin type plays a huge role in picking the perfect one! Here’s how to find your ideal match from Dot & Key’s sunscreen range:

✅ For Normal Skin: Go for the Vitamin C+E SPF 50+ pa ++++ Sunscreen! It's fluidy texture absorbs quickly, feels super lightweight, and gives your skin a radiant glow. Perfect if you want sun protection with added brightness and reduce dullness and darkspots ! ✨

✅ For Oily & Combination Skin: The Watermelon Cooling SPF 50+ pa++++ Sunscreen is a game-changer! It’s non-sticky, non-greasy, and gives an instant cooling effect, making it perfect for those who struggle with excess oil or shine. 🍉💦This also provides protection against uv,infrared and Bluelight.

✅ For Dry Skin: Your best bet is the Blueberry Hydrate Barrier Repair SPF 50+ pa ++++ Sunscreen.It has 7 uv filters with hyaluronic acid and ceramides.It provides deep hydration, strengthens the skin barrier, and locks in moisture, so your skin feels soft and protected all day long! 🫐💧

All three variants are fragrance 🆓 

Sunscreen is a must-have, but choosing the right one makes all the difference! So, which one is made for your skin?
